R.O., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEPT. OF CHILDREN & FAMILIES, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D19-0169 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. May 2, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Because R. O. has failed to serve an initial brief as provided by this court's order of March 19, 2019, this appeal is dismissed for failure to prosecute.

VILLANTI, SALARIO, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
